author: tajrussell
body: Adding a new ONNX model for PAIReD Jets (https://indico.cern.ch/event/1372046/contributions/5993835/attachments/2874191/5033020/BTV_PAIReD.pdf). Simultaneously making a PR to CMSSW (https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/45207) that requires this model. This model is not the final product, training is still being perfected. This model is for testing only.
title: New paired onnx model
